main event: An unidentified observation was reported in Farmville, Virginia on 24 July 1966.
interesting points: The conclusion of the report stated there was insufficient data for evaluation., The observation involved a ground visual observation that appeared to move vertically., The reporting process included detailed questions for the observers about their sighting., The report included mentions of follow-up correspondence from the Air Force regarding the insufficient details., There were references to multiple forms and questionnaires associated with documenting UFO sightings.
